{"article_id":"qGOerD4ZmvhD2j20","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"On Saturday , reports began flowing out of Syria","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that their own government allegedly had used chemical attacks on civilians","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"which killed dozens of men , women , and children .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"It was unknown what the response from the United States would be ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"but today President Donald J. Trump made clear","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that he is blaming Russian President Vladimir Putin and the Iranian government for supporting `` Animal Assad . ''","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"From The Telegraph :","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"`` Syrian opposition activists and rescuers said Sunday","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"that a poison gas attack on a rebel-held town near the capital has killed at least 49 people , according to local estimates .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"The allegations are denied by the Syrian government ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"with the US describing the reports as `` horrifying '' .","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"A joint statement by the medical relief organisation Syrian American Medical Society","depth":15},{"id":12,"text":"( SAMS )","depth":15},{"id":13,"text":"and the civil defence service ,","depth":15},{"id":14,"text":"which operates in rebel-held areas ,","depth":15},{"id":15,"text":"said","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"49 people had died in the attack late on Saturday .","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"Others put the toll at 150 or more .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"A Syrian rebel group accused government forces of dropping a barrel bomb","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"containing poisonous chemicals on civilians in eastern Ghouta ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"with one rescue group reporting more than 150 deaths .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Syrian state media denied","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"government forces had launched any chemical attack","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"rebels in the eastern Ghouta town of Douma were in a state of collapse","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and spreading false news .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The US State Department said","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"the reports of mass casualties were `` horrifying ''","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and would demand an international response","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"if confirmed ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"laying some of the blame with Russia . ''","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Gruesome videos of the deceased started to appear across social media platforms .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Many of the images are unbearable to look at .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Here is one of the horrifying videos","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"coming out of Douma in Syria tonight","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"showing the aftermath of what seems to be a chemical gas attack .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"These people were hiding underground from the bombing ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"leaving them more vulnerable to gas .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"pic.twitter.com/mm9jgBZ4V8","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"- Liz Sly","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"( @ LizSly )","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"April 7 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Sorry please forgive me","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"I have to share this photos .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"In case you didn ' t know ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"this is happening in # Syria today ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"children gassed to death . # Douma","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"pic.twitter.com/tMOsz1BPXp","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"- Fatemah Alabed","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"( @ FatemahAlabed )","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"April 8 , 2018 .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"@ DevinNunes on the chemical attack in Syria :","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"\" I haven ' t been briefed on this yet...","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"but obviously it ' s very troubling. \"","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"pic.twitter.com/3mvuC74CMX","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"- Fox News","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"( @ FoxNews )","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"April 8 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"After these reports became public ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"the commander in chief took to twitter","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"there will be a `` big price to pay '' for those responsible .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"After these reports became public ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"the commander in chief took to twitter","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"there will be a `` big price to pay '' for those responsible .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Many dead ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"including women and children ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"in mindless CHEMICAL attack in Syria .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Area of atrocity is in lockdown and encircled by Syrian Army ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"making it completely inaccessible to outside world .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"President Putin , Russia and Iran are responsible","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"for backing Animal Assad .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Big price ...","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"April 8 , 2018","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":".... to pay .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Open area immediately for medical help and verification .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Another humanitarian disaster for no reason whatsoever .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"SICK !","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"April 8 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"President Trump quickly followed that sentiment up","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"by referring to President Obama 's infamous `` red line '' comments regarding Syria 's use of chemical weapons .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"President Obama promised to intervene in Syria","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"if Assad used chemical weapons","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"but","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"when the time came ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"he failed to follow through on that promise .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"From PBS :","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"`` In August of 2013 , a rebel-held suburb of Damascus was attacked with sarin gas","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"- a nerve agent","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"that causes lung muscle paralysis","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"and results in death from suffocation .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"The attack killed 1,400 men , women and children ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"and at the White House , officials asserted \" with high confidence \"","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"that the government of Bashar al-Assad was responsible .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"One year earlier , President Barack Obama had described Assad ' s potential use of chemical weapons as \" a red line \"","depth":3},{"id":100,"text":"that would have \" enormous consequences \"","depth":4},{"id":101,"text":"and \" change my calculus \" on American military intervention in Syria ' s civil war .","depth":4},{"id":102,"text":"When Assad appeared to cross that line ,","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"Obama ordered the Pentagon to prepare to attack .","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"\" Our finger was on the trigger , \"","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"Gen. Martin Dempsey , Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff , tells veteran FRONTLINE correspondent Martin Smith in tomorrow ' s new documentary , Obama at War .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"\" We had everything in place","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"and we were just waiting for instructions","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"to proceed. \"","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"as FRONTLINE details in the below excerpt from Obama at War ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"the president had second thoughts .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"\" The president was looking for a way","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"to not have to make good on the threat","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that he had made , \"","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Col. Andrew Bacevich","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"( Ret . ) ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"author of The Limits of Power , tells FRONTLINE .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"because the president","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"having drawn that red line","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"realized","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"that he had no appetite for direct military engagement in Syria . \"","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"On that subject , President Trump asserted","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"Syria could have ended long ago","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"if President Obama followed through with his promise .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":251,"left":224,"right":250,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":191,"right":223,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":131,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":128,"right":130,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":0,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":3,"right":129,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":129,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":190,"left":155,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":150,"right":154,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":145,"right":149,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":6,"right":144,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":144,"left":141,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":132,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"